**Layers generated:**
1. `start` — CEO spawn point in executive office
2. `floor` — Light grey office flooring (tile 201), darker carpet areas (tile 223), wood accents (tile 141)
3. `walls` — Outer walls and room dividers using tileset1 wall tiles (45, 58, 63, 73)
4. `furniture` — Desks, chairs, monitors, bookshelves from tileset1, tileset5_export, tileset6_export
5. `furniture_above` — Items that render above the player (top of bookshelves, overhead lights)
6. `collision` — Invisible collision layer for walls and solid furniture
7. `jitsiMeetingRoom` — Jitsi zones in Boardroom and Meeting Rooms (tile 454 from Special_Zones)
8. `decorations` — Plants, awards, posters, corporate branding elements
9. `glass_walls` — Semi-transparent glass partitions for boardroom and modern rooms

